^ Per Adam Siljeström, The educational institutions of the United States, their character and organization, J. Chapman, 1853, p. 243: "Influence of European emigration on the state of civilization in the United States: Statistics of popular culture in America".John Morley在1876年在伯明翰市政廳的演說《On Popular Culture》就是指較低階層的教育程度
^ Rabelais and Bakhtin: Popular Culture in "Gargantua and Pantagruel" p.13
